profile:
Residential and Commercial Moving and Storage, Packing and Unpacking Services.

As professional Firefighters, each day we rely on a commitment to teamwork, safety and integrity to provide our communities with emergency services when they need them most.

Applying these same principles to the Residential Moving Industry has allowed us to create a company that provides Ontario with the highest standards of moving and storage services. Why Firemen Movers? We are Safe, Dependable, Hard Working and On-time!

Our commitment to quality working practices ensures that everyone involved in your move is a trained, properly equipped and certified employee. We do not use day labor or contract out, which ensures that we can move your belongings quickly and safely. In addition to exceptionally high service levels we also support 2 important local charities, The Sick Kids Burn Unit, and the Red Door Family Shelter.

Call now to learn more about our Ontario moving services and receive a FREE, no obligation estimate for your move.

Hercules Moving Company Inc is a Toronto based moving company which provides high-quality household moving, commercial relocation, piano moving and storage services. 
Hercules Moving Company Inc operates in the Greater Toronto Area and offers a full moving service, including packing and unpacking services.
In addition to packing services, Hercules also offers full disassembly, and reassembly of any furniture during any move. Whether you are moving locally or simply moving a piano, Hercules Moving Company will come fully insured and bonded.
The company stands out from other moving companies Toronto, ON with its unique wrapping and packing methods which reliably protect items during the move. 
Hercules Moving Company Inc is also a long distance and cross Canada mover that provides moving services from as  far West as Vancouver Island to as far East as St. John’s, Newfoundland .

profile:
Aleks moving started in 2007 with family at the core, we are family owned and operated and we put that care we have for our own family into the care we show for our clients and their belongings. Moving can be stressful so we ensure we take the time to do a walkthrough with you, to carefully pack (if needed)  and load/unload your belongings safely and carefully.

 During these times we also work to ensure all of our staff are equipped with the proper safety gear and that our moving equipment and trucks are cleaned and sanitized prior to your move, we also offer FLAT RATE FEE and offer 24/7 care and service. We offer the best rates in Ontario. CALL US TODAY FOR A FREE ESTIMATE


• All staff are equipped and trained with safety gear, such as masks, gloves, clothing + hand sanitizer
• Aleks Moving has implemented strict and extensive cleaning and sanitizing practices for all our moving equipment like blankets and straps, and the interior and exterior of our trucks
• We are constantly monitoring each staff for symptoms and encouraging them to stay home if they are not feeling well
• One person social distancing walk through of your home prior to your move to ensure everything is clear and understood. 

Please stay safe , wash yours hands often and practice social distancing. 

Free estimates at your convenience, including coming out to your home to view what you have to move so we have a better understanding so that on the day of the move there are no surprises for you or the movers. packing and unpacking if required, protection of all furniture, dismantling and reassembling, short and long-term storage, inventory service, and many other services.

profile:
Quality service at an affordable price.

Our local movers can handle moves of any size, including apartments, condos, single-family homes, retirement communities, dorms and more. VR MOVING is also specialized in moving any size of pianos, safes. When you move with us, you know your things will be safe. When you choose VR Moving, you know you’ll always get:
Upfront rates, with no hidden fees
On-time service
Friendly, uniformed movers

When you arrange for a move with us, we’ll take care of everything. From showing up on time to keeping your costs as low as possible, you can feel confident that your project is in good hands. 
With over five  years of experience, in 2021 we started VR MOVING INC. While moving can be very stressful and can’t be cheap, the last thing people need is the unfair & over priced cost of a “professional” moving services. We believe there is a way to provide valuable, honest and professional moving services at an affordable prices. We're very excited to serve our community and we are committed to provide honest services.

IMPORTANT TO KNOW
- We always provide  written estimates that can be completed either in your home or over the phone, whichever is best for you. All estimates are free of cost.
- We do not surprise you with hidden charges at the time of final payment.
- We provide top notch service at reasonable prices

Why Should you feel comfortable in selecting us?
The processes we follow ensure you will receive a consistent result designed to exceed your expectations, reduce your stress levels and deliver you a happy comfortable experience.
Through our services we provide you tailor made solutions based on your needs, not out of the box offered to everyone.
We are local and family run, readily available to help you.
Our people are trained in a way that ensures you feel secure knowing your belongings are treated like they are our own.

QUESTIONS YOU SHOULD ASK EVERY COMPANY
1) Who Are You?
- We are a locally owned and operated family run business based in Mississauga, Ontario.   We are not your typical moving, storage or junk removal company.  We are a unique “One Stop ” solution for home owners and businesses.   We created Space Makers to help our clients run their lives and businesses with less stress and more comfort through less clutter.
We are “The simple solution to your Home’s (or businesses) evolution”

2) What Services Do You Offer?
- We offer the following:
Local moving – we pad, wrap and protect your belongings like they were our own.
Storage – we will remove and store items you do not need right now but may need in the future.
Junk – we will remove items you no longer need.
Donation or Auction – we will remove items you no longer need but do not want to see go to waste.
In home moving – for staging or simply rearranging, let us do the heavy lifting for you

3) What Do You Believe and why do you do what you do?
- We believe that no two client situations are the same.
- We believe that clients desire a “one stop” solution for their space making needs rather than dealing with numerous different service -providers.
- We believe that by properly analyzing the needs of our clients through client friendly conversation we will accurately understand their specific objectives.
- We believe that our clients deserve customized solutions with transparent quotes based on their specific objectives.
- We believe that by delivering quality and on-going training for all of our employees we will be an employer of choice for professional and personable employees.
- We believe that by having well-trained, professional and personable employees deliver a customized solution based on our understanding of our client’s objectives, we will be the “gold standard” for residential and commercial moving and storage.

4) Who do you work with?
- Our clients are just like you. We work with residential home-owners and renters to assist them with their local moves and with space-creation needs within their homes. 
- We also work with Business clients helping them with their moving and storage requirements.

5) What makes you different?
A) Our company
- Unique, not your average moving, storage or junk removal company.
- Local
- the simple solution to your home or business’s evolution.

B) Our Solutions
- Unique – tailored to your needs.
- Diverse, one stop company to reduce stress, save you time and money.
- Consistent, reliable, we follow our processes in every step.

C) Our People
- Well trained, professional and personable.
- Family run. We treat you and our team like they are our family - they are!
- Integrity, we were founded based on our core business beliefs including transparency and honesty.

Our Experience

services:
Local Movers​
To offer the best moving home services, Coraza Movers has staff members with a host of skills in electrical installations, carpentry, plumbing and house-keeping. We invest in training to ensure the staff are equipped with emerging trends in the moving industry.

We provide all the necessary packing materials to ensure no damages to your furniture. Our vehicles are custom built for carrying items that need care and safety, they are padded on the inside to minimize damage, and they have lashing rails for tying and fastening the items.

Long Distance Movers
A majority of our moves are done for the local area’s residents, we also can work long distances too, when you ask us to!

Office Movers
